Package: LongitudinalSmarter
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Longitudinal Mixed-Effects Models for Microbiome Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Leran", "Wang", email = "leranwang10@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a streamlined workflow for fitting mixed-effects models to
    longitudinal microbiome data (presence/absence and abundance). Automatically
    extracts reference group trajectories, non-reference group trajectories, and
    between-group contrasts at each timepoint. Includes visualization tools for
    generating heatmaps of significant results.
